封城后的湖北荆州：医用级防护物资存量告急。
Hubei Jingzhou: the stock of medical-grade protective materials is in urgent need.
作者：邹黄晶 张玉 来源：中国经营网。
Author: Zou Huangjing Zhang Yu Source: China Business Network.
特约撰稿 邹黄晶 本报记者 张玉 荆州、上海报道“我们已经想尽了一切办法，目前最缺的还是医用级口罩、防护服、护目镜等，只能尽量保证隔离病房和发热门诊。
"We have done everything we can to ensure medical masks, protective clothing, goggles, etc. and can only ensure the isolation ward and the fever clinic," said Zhang Yingzhou, a reporter for the newspaper Zou Huang Jing and Shanghai
”2月3日，荆州市第二人民医院工会的翁主任向《中国经营报》记者表示。
On February 3, Weng director of the Second People's Hospital trade union in Jingzhou told China Business Daily.
最新数据显示，2020年2月2日0时～24时，湖北省新增新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎病例2103例，其中荆州市166例，在全省15个市中位列第4位。
The latest figures show that between 0000 and 2400 hours on February 2, 2020, there were 2,103 new cases of pneumonia infected with the coronavirus in Hubei Province, 166 of which were in Jingzhou City, ranking fourth among the 15 cities in the province.
截至2020年2月2日24时，湖北省累计报告新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎病例11177例，其中荆州市499例，在全省位列第5位。
As of 2400 hours February 2, 2020, a total of 11,177 cases of pneumonia with new coronavirus infection have been reported in Hubei Province, including 499 cases, ranking fifth in the province.
随着疫情的不断蔓延，做好医疗防护物资的收治和调配，保证医疗防护物资供应的攻坚战正在打响。
With the spread of the epidemic, to do a good job of medical protection material reception and deployment, to ensure the supply of medical protection supplies is starting.
有绿色通道 缺少合格的医用物资本报记者获取的一份荆州市第二人民医院新型冠状病毒肺炎防控用品受捐需求表显示，该院医用外科口罩、医用防护口罩、医用一次性防护服、84消毒液、水银体温计、医用红外温度计、护目镜、手术衣、防护面罩(头罩)、手消毒液、长鞋套、75%酒精(500mL)、磷酸奥司他韦胶囊及盐酸比多尔分散片等多种防护物资及药品均呈现物资紧张的状况。
The medical surgical mask, medical mask, medical disposable protective clothing, 84 disinfectant, mercury thermometer, medical infrared thermometer, goggles, surgical coat, protective mask (hood), hand sanitizer, shoe cover, 75% alcohol (500mL), oseltamivir phosphate capsule and Bidol hydrochloride dispersible tablet are under material strain.
其中，仅各种类型的医用口罩需求量就达到11万个。
The demand for all types of medical masks alone is 110,000.
图片由受访者提供2月3日中午11﹕30，荆州市第二人民医院一位专门负责捐赠事宜的工作人员向记者表示：“这张表上的部分物资通过各种渠道已经到位，但目前最大的问题还是医用级防护口罩、医用级防护服、医用眼罩以及医用面罩，这几种防护用品目前我们存量非常少。
"Some of the materials on this list are already in place through various channels, but the biggest problem is medical-grade face masks, medical-grade suits, medical eye masks and medical masks," a donation worker at Jingzhou Second People's Hospital told reporters.
”这位工作人员向记者介绍：“N95级别有很多种不同的应用场景，比如防花粉的、防雾霾的，这也是我们强调要医用级N95口罩的原因之一。
"The N95 comes in many different applications, such as pollen and haze, which is one of the reasons we emphasize medical N95 masks," the official told reporters.
另外，不管是国标还是其他国家标准，只要是给一线用的，都必须是医用场景的。
In addition, whether national standards or other national standards, as long as it is for the first line, must be the medical scene.
”上述工作人员坦言，其实收到了一些其他的N95口罩，但只能给二线、三线的医护人员使用，医用级别的非常紧缺。
The staff admitted they had received some other N95 masks, but only for second- and third-line medical staff, who were in dire need of a medical grade.
除了荆州市第二人民医院，荆州市另一家新冠肺炎定点医院——荆州市第一人民医院负责物资捐赠的一位负责人向记者直言：“目前医院最缺的是国标19083的医用级N95口罩和19082标准的防护服。
"What the hospital is missing most are 19083 medical-grade N95 masks and 19082 standard protective clothing," said a director of the Jingzhou First People's Hospital, another designated hospital for pneumonia in Jingzhou.
”而在荆州市下辖的监利县，这个全市距离此次疫情暴发中心的武汉市最近的县，防护物资存量同样不容乐观。
In Jingzhou's prison county, the closest prefecture to Wuhan, the epicentre of the outbreak, stocks of protective materials are no better.
监利县中医医院一位内部人士向记者透露，很多物资都是由一些民间组织机构、个人直接捐到中医院，当然红十字会也会下拨物资。
A person inside the hospital told reporters that many materials are donated directly to the hospital by some non-governmental organizations and individuals, although the Red Cross will also allocate materials.
他表示：“医用防护服、护目镜，我们都是供给一线，现有的物资收一批用一批，有的还能用几天，有的已经没有了，像能上一线的医用防护口罩以及防护服。
"Medical protective clothing, goggles, we are the supply line, existing supplies from a batch, some can be used for a few days, some are no longer available, such as can be a first-line medical mask and protective clothing.
”此外，荆州市几家医院的工作人员都表示，目前有绿色通道，只是缺少合格的医用物资。
In addition, staff at several hospitals in Jingzhou said there was a "green passage" but a shortage of qualified medical supplies.
记者就志愿者防护物资进城问题致电荆州市新冠(新型)肺炎防控指挥部，对方表示：“指挥部这边目前只负责文件上传下达，物资捐赠、开具通行证明需由当地交通运输局，也就是指挥部交通组所在地负责。
"At present, the command post is only responsible for the transmission of documents. The local transportation bureau, the headquarters' transportation unit, is responsible for the donation and issuance of transit certificates," the spokesman said.
”荆州市红十字会对社会捐赠每日公示“疫情刚开始的一段时间，全国各地都有人找我要求购买医用N95口罩，甚至还有孕妇找我购买医用防护服。
"In the early days of the epidemic, people from all over the country asked me to buy medical N95 masks, and pregnant women even asked me to buy medical protective clothing.
”江西南昌一位口罩代理商向记者表示，由于春节假期这一季节性因素，不少口罩工厂恢复生产还需要时间。
A mask agent in Nanchang, Jiangxi, told reporters it would take time for many mask factories to resume production because of the seasonal nature of the holiday.
“大约初九初十能基本恢复生产。
"About the tenth day of the ninth basic resumption of production.
生产恢复较慢除了用工难，还有原材料短缺等因素。
The slow recovery in production is due to factors such as labour shortages and shortages of raw materials.
”不过，她向记者表示：“从上级经销商处了解到，防护用品和消毒用品已经列为政府管控物资(军需物资)，主要供给一线。
However, she told reporters: "I have heard from higher dealers that protective and disinfectant supplies are already listed as government controlled goods (quartermaster supplies), the main supply line.
”图片由受访者提供，南昌当地一家较大的防控用品生产基地需向当地政府报备生产情况2月1日，荆州市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎防控指挥部召开会议，安排部署下阶段全市疫情防控工作。
A large local production base in Nanchang province was asked to report production to the local government on Feb. 1, 2007. The Pneumonia Command for the New Coronavirus Infection in Jingzhou City held a meeting to arrange the next phase of the city-wide epidemic prevention and control.
市长崔永辉在发言中强调，各地各部门要把社会捐赠款物管好用好，准确掌握数据、分配去向等信息。
Mayor Cui Yonghui stressed in his speech that departments around the world should keep good control of social donations, accurate data distribution and other information.
要高度关注重点区域，对于离武汉近、人口众多、医疗资源相对薄弱的县市区，在力量分配和物资调配上要给予倾斜。
We should pay high attention to key areas, and give preferential treatment to counties and cities close to Wuhan, with large population and weak medical resources.
要坚决克服麻痹思想和侥幸心理，从严从实做好隐患排查，对暴露出来的问题要及时整改，确保防控工作主动及时、措施到位、处置有效。
We should resolutely overcome inconveniences and chances of success, strictly carry out hidden dangers and correct problems in time to ensure that prevention and control work is carried out in a timely manner, measures in place and effective disposal.
2月3日，记者从荆州市中心医院一位工作人员处了解到，医疗防护物资一直在接收，具体数字还在统计之中。
Feb. 3, the reporter from a staff member of Jingzhou Central Hospital, the medical protection material has been receiving, the number is still in statistics.
她还向记者表示：“目前我们筹资防护物资主要还是依靠自筹、企业与个人的社会捐赠、红十字会调拨三种渠道。
"At present, we mainly rely on self-financing, corporate and individual social donations, Red Cross allocation three channels," she told reporters.
”她向记者坦言：“最近的物资捐赠接收要合理很多，可以直接寄到医院，也可以通过红十字会指定某家医院。
"Recent donations are much more reasonably received and can be sent directly to a hospital or designated through the Red Cross," she told reporters.
”图片来自荆州市红十字会微信公众号截图，昨晚9点除了发布本级红十字会部分资金去向外，还对接收的物资、资金进行了公示另据了解，目前荆州市红十字会仍是本市最大物资中转站。
The Red Cross Society of Jingzhou City is still the city's largest transit centre for goods, according to a map released by the Red Cross Society of Jingzhou at 9: 00 pm last night.
荆州市红十字会相关人士向记者表示：“目前防护物资进城是有绿色通道的，拉这些医疗物资的货车经过检查后一般是不拦的，如果货车出城遇到问题，我们一般就开个通行证。
"At present, there is a green passage for the entry of protective materials into the city," Red Cross officials told reporters. "The trucks that pull these medical supplies are usually checked without stopping.
”不过，这位红十字会工作人员向记者表示：“如果企业或者个人准备了某一批物资或者资金指定捐赠给荆州市某家医院，我们会先做一个入库登记，然后通知(捐赠人指定)医院领取。
However, the Red Cross official told reporters: "If an enterprise or individual prepares a specific batch of materials or funds earmarked for donation to a hospital in Jingzhou, we will first make a warehousing registration and then inform the (donor-designated) hospital to collect it.
”记者发现，荆州市红十字会对于社会捐赠情况、上级调拨情况在官方微信公众号上进行了每日公示。
The reporter found that the Jingzhou Red Cross Society made daily announcements on the official micro-letter public sign about social donations and the allocation of higher-level posts.
(编辑：石英婧 校对：颜京宁)。
